text.tspan: Runtime model counting performance (medians across 86 samples) of Dagster
(w/ decompositions A and B, w/ TiniSAT (T) and MiniSAT (M) cores) against
TiniSAT, Lingeling, MiniSAT, Painless-Mcomsps, Paracooba, DMC and Dsyrup
solvers, for nxn superproblem arrays of 15x15 pentomino subproblems.
